<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Monthly Income Prediction - AgriFlow</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/agriflow.css">
    <style>
        .income-result-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .income-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .income-display {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .income-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .monthly-chart {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .month-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .month-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .month-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            min-width: 100px;
        }

        .month-bar {
            flex: 1;
            height: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            padding-right: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .month-income {
            min-width: 100px;
            text-align: right;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .summary-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .summary-value {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .summary-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .btn-next {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #e8f4f8;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .info-box strong {
            color: #667eea;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .summary-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .income-display {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .month-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .month-bar {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 8px 0;
                min-width: 200px;
            }

            .month-income {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: left;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar-agriflow') %>

        <section class="section">
            <div class="income-result-container">
                <h2>🎯 Your Income Prediction</h2>
                <p>आपकी मासिक आय का पूर्वानुमान / Based on your farm details</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Farmer Info Card -->
            <div class="income-card">
                <h3>👨‍🌾 Farm Details</h3>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <div>
                        <div class="income-label">नाम / Name</div>
                        <p><strong><%= farmer.name %></strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="income-label">जिला / District</div>
                        <p><strong><%= farmer.district %></strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="income-label">फसल / Crop</div>
                        <p><strong><%= farmer.crop %></strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="income-label">जमीन / Land Size</div>
                        <p><strong><%= farmer.land %> एकड़ / acres</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Main Income Prediction -->
            <div class="income-card">
                <div class="income-label">💰 Average Monthly Income</div>
                <div class="income-display">₹<%= farmer.averageMonthlyIncome %></div>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                    📊 Based on your <%= farmer.land %> acre(s) of <%= farmer.crop %> cultivation
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Real Data Factors Used in Prediction -->
            <div class="income-card">
                <h3>🔍 Real Data Factors Used</h3>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <div class="income-label">🌧️ Rainfall</div>
                        <p><strong><%= typeof farmer.rainfall !== 'undefined' ? farmer.rainfall.toFixed(1) : 'N/A' %> mm</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <div class="income-label">🌱 NDVI (Vegetation Index)</div>
                        <p><strong><%= typeof farmer.ndvi !== 'undefined' ? farmer.ndvi.toFixed(3) : 'N/A' %></strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <div class="income-label">📈 Mandi Price</div>
                        <p><strong>₹<%= typeof farmer.mandiPrice !== 'undefined' ? farmer.mandiPrice : 'N/A' %>/quintal</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <div class="income-label">📊 Price Shock</div>
                        <p><strong><%= typeof farmer.priceShock !== 'undefined' ? (farmer.priceShock > 0 ? '+' : '') + farmer.priceShock.toFixed(2) : 'N/A' %>%</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Summary Cards -->
            <div class="summary-grid">
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="summary-label">🏆 Best Earning Month</div>
                    <div class="summary-value"><%= farmer.bestMonth %></div>
                    <div style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px;">₹<%= farmer.bestMonthIncome %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="summary-label">📉 Lowest Month</div>
                    <div class="summary-value"><%= farmer.lowestMonth %></div>
                    <div style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 8px;">₹<%= farmer.lowestMonthIncome %></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Monthly Income Chart -->
            <div class="income-card">
                <h3>📅 Monthly Income Breakdown</h3>
                <div class="monthly-chart">
                    <% farmer.monthlyIncomeData.forEach((item, index) => { %>
                        <div class="month-item">
                            <div class="month-name"><%= item.month %></div>
                            <div class="month-bar" style="width: <%= (item.income / farmer.bestMonthIncome * 100) %>%; min-width: 50px;">
                                <%= Math.round((item.income / farmer.bestMonthIncome * 100)) %>%
                            </div>
                            <div class="month-income">₹<%= item.income.toLocaleString('en-IN') %></div>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Info Box -->
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>💡 कैसे किया गया यह अनुमान? / How was this prediction made?</strong><br>
                हमारे AI मॉडल ने वास्तविक डेटा का उपयोग करके आपकी आय का अनुमान लगाया है:
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px;">
                    <li>🌧️ वास्तविक वर्षा डेटा (Actual Rainfall)</li>
                    <li>🌱 NDVI वनस्पति सूचकांक (Vegetation Health)</li>
                    <li>📈 मंडी में फसल का वर्तमान मूल्य (Market Price)</li>
                    <li>📊 कीमत में बदलाव (Price Shock)</li>
                    <li>📅 पिछली महीनों की आय (Historical Income)</li>
                </ul>
                <strong>Your average monthly income is approximately ₹<%= farmer.averageMonthlyIncome %>.</strong> You can plan your loan EMI
                based on this income using real agricultural data and machine learning model.
            </div>

            <!-- Action Buttons -->
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/agriflow/apply" class="btn-next btn-primary">
                    📊 Plan My Loan →
                </a>
                <a href="/agriflow/monthly-income" class="btn-next btn-secondary">
                    🔄 Try Again
                </a>
                <a href="/agriflow" class="btn-next btn-secondary">
                    🏠 Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <%- include('partials/footer-agriflow') %>
</body>

</html>
